sentences.english: While stock last for the free copies of HK Telecom Story Book.

sentences.english: Complemented with a rhodium plated chain.
The 26 pop-ups on the poster are a nice bonus.
sentences.chinese: 海报上的26个弹出的卡片是额外附送的。

sentences.english: Beautiful handcrafted musical pendant for mom-to-be to wear as necklace, with the pendant resting low on her belly.
sentences.chinese: 准妈妈佩戴附送的项链，音乐球会自然下垂至腹部。

sentences.english: The detailed package inserts supplied with medicines have long been a familiar feature of pharmaceuticals.
sentences.chinese: 随药品附送的详细包装插页更是司空见惯。

sentences.english: Mother always buys things in stores where they give trading stamps.
sentences.chinese: 母亲总是附送赠券的店里买东西。

sentences.english: As an added bonus, much of the code needed to begin data extraction is included with this article.
sentences.chinese: 另外，本文还附送了许多开始数据抽取所需的代码。

sentences.english: All of these looked really good to my eyes, which were covered by the included black 3D shades.
sentences.chinese: 用随机附送的黑色3D眼镜观看，效果均非常不错。

sentences.english: Howard: Yeah, but it comes with a little coin purse.
sentences.chinese: 没错，但它附送一个零钱包呢。

sentences.english: Send a regular copy of your resume along with the scannable version.
sentences.chinese: 发送普通的简历，并附送一份易于扫描的版本。
